<h3><i class="fa fa-info-circle"></i> Info</h3>
<p>This is the <strong>Info</strong> tab content.</p>
<p>This boilerplate demonstrates the "GrayGate" pattern (Method 2) for creating a custom admin tool page that is robust and language-prefix safe.</p>
<ul>
    <li>The sidebar entry is added in <code>onAdminMenu()</code>.</li>
    <li>The route is intercepted in <code>onAdminPageInitialized()</code> by the <code>onAdminPageInterceptor()</code> method.</li>
    <li>The controller at <code>classes/Admin/ToolBoilerplateAdminController.php</code> handles the request and sets the active tab.</li>
    <li>This tabbed UI is rendered by <code>admin/templates/r4it-tool-boilerplate.html.twig</code>.</li>
</ul>
